Job Description
Pixarch Pakistan’s leading architectural visualization company looking for a talented, enthusiastic, and organized artist for the post of 3D architectural visualizer. The ideal candidate will have a strong working knowledge of 3D Studio Max, V-ray, and Photoshop with a minimum of 6 years of professional experience in a related position.
Job Specification
Strong command on modeling, texturing, lighting, rendering and animation in 3DS Max & V-rayAutoCAD knowledge is also preferred.At least 6 Years of experienceExcellent Photoshop skills.Experience with animation post-processing software such as After Effects preferred but not essential.Ability to work independently and within a team to meet tight deadlines.Strong communication skills, time management, and self-driven work ethic.Independent and also manage the team.
